aVThe history of science has been one long series of violent brainstorms,
p59
aVas successive generations have come to terms with
p60
aVincreasing levels of queerness in the universe.
p61
aVWe're now so used to the idea that the Earth spins,
p62
aVrather than the Sun moves across the sky,
p63
aVit's hard for us to realize
p64
aVwhat a shattering mental revolution that must have been.
p65
