aVA monkey's brain must have software capable of simulating
p232
aVa three-dimensional world of branches and trunks.
p233
aVA mole's software for constructing models of its world will be customized
p234
aVfor underground use.
p235
aVA water strider's brain doesn't need 3D software at all,
p236
aVsince it lives on the surface of the pond,
p237
aVin an Edwin Abbott flatland.
